data.description: Welcome to this exquisite single-story home, nestled on 1.74 acres. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms, a study/office, 3.5 bathrooms, gas fireplace and a split 3-car garage, this home spans over 3600 sq ft of luxurious living space. Designed with impeccable attention to detail, the open floor plan showcases designer touches throughout, making it resemble a model home. The chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a gas cooktop, expansive island, walk-in pantry, tons of cabinets/counter space and stainless steel appliances. Ideal for entertaining, the layout seamlessly flows from the kitchen to the living areas. The owner's retreat is a sanctuary of comfort, offering his & her closets, separate vanities, and a double-head walk-thru shower, complemented by a 6 ft oversized tub. Additional features include bedrooms with a jack & jill bath and a guest suite with a private bath. A media room provides entertainment, while the absence of an HOA allows for freedom in the backyard oasis. With breathtaking views and limitless potential, this home is a must-see. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your forever home.
